            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* This is a coordinated national request being submitted to multiple Members of Congress.\n* Submissions are being directed to offices representing districts with significant NASA Science Mission Directorate (SMD) investments.\n* In the House, the request is supported by Reps. Don Bacon (R-NE) and Judy Chu (D-CA).",
