            "field_type": "textarea",
            "required": true,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* This request is a $1.75 billion increase (24%) over the FY2026 enacted level of $7.25 billion.\n* Because the FY2027 President's Budget Request has not yet been released, this request establishes a $9 billion target based on scientific requirements.\n* The requested $9 billion is essential to recover from workforce losses and maintain the competitive edge of the U.S. space program.",
